<L>__{exterior devil's cauldron various angles night}
<A>__{the temperature dips as the winds shifts and blows down from the north. another storm approaches. the temperate days of last week seem ages ago. kenai, neff, and other townsmen batten devil's cauldron down for the storm. kenai is bundled up in the cold. the men tighten guy wires on the radio tower, windmills and caches; bring firewood indoors; close off unused rooms in the general store and spa. then neff and kenai split off from the others.}
